# packforge — Windsurf Rules

## Project Context
Turborepo monorepo for an AI Agent Instruction Hub. Orchestrates context-aware instruction packs for MCP-compatible agents.

## Stack
- TypeScript 5.8 strict mode with `exactOptionalPropertyTypes`
- Turborepo, Zod, MCP SDK v1.10, Vitest

## Key Conventions
- Use conditional spread for optional properties: `...(val ? { val } : {})`
- YAML packs validated via `npm run validate:packs`
- Run `npm run ci` before committing

## Architecture
- apps/context-analyzer — project analysis
- apps/orchestrator — pack matching
- apps/mcp-gateway — MCP stdio server
- packages/shared-types — Zod schemas
- packs/ — 17 YAML instruction packs

## GitNexus
This repo is indexed. Use impact analysis before editing. Use detect_changes before committing.
